data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF! Back on market because the buyer could not obtain financing. Come tour this welcoming home in Sonterra! With a spacious living room and dedicated downstairs office, this home has the perfect set up. Freshly painted kitchen cabinets add a warm touch to the eat-in dining area as well as the entertainer's backyard. The massive back patio is perfect for all your family or entertaining needs. This section of Sonterra has much larger and private backyards than any other section! All bedroom are upstairs, as well as a second living room or kids playroom space. Come see this beautiful home today! For VA buyers- the seller's loan is assumable at 2.75%. Please reach out to the listing agent for details.
